      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"7. LITTLE CLIFFY filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Electric Man (19.02) in a Mix 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to feature in the finish again. 3. ELECTRIC MAN was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by a nose at this track in a handy 19.01. Fair draw can see a good run and has a good record over this journey. One of the key runners again. 1. JUST LIKE NU showed strong pace early from the inside rail and stuck on well despite missing the frame, finishing sixth over 350m this track in 19.54. Has the ability to give this a shake. 2. STRIKES TWICE scored last time and can measure up again.\",\"runners\":[7,3,1,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
